Package: phat
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Software to compute persistence pairs
 This software library contains methods for computing the persistence
 pairs of a  filtered cell complex represented by an ordered
 boundary matrix with Z_2 coefficients. 

Package: libphat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Software to compute persistence pairs (development files)
 This software library contains methods for computing the persistence
 pairs of a  filtered cell complex represented by an ordered
 boundary matrix with Z_2 coefficients. 
